                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7968" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1996</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当老专家撞上新世代：邦天农业该不该继续加大投资？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Old Experts Collide With The New Generation ：Should Bangtian Agriculture Continue to Increase Investment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董梦杭，陈珊珊，赵文葵，乜堪雄，巫艾玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当老专家撞上新世代：邦天农业该不该继续加大投资</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农业企业；战略选择；新老世代管理者；不确定环境；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Agricultural enterprises; Strategic choices; New and old generation managers; Uncertain environment </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新老世代决策冲突问题是现代管理学的常见问题之一。重庆邦天农业发展有限公司旗下的彩色森林项目当前由两个世代共同管理，当外部环境面临巨大变化时，新老世代管理者无论在思维还是实战上都会有所不同。本案例从巫艾玲董事长的角度出发，描述了在疫情的冲击下，邦天农业营收骤减，公司新老世代管理者在是否继续加大投资这一问题上的决策冲突。老专家坚持不能继续加大投资，认为企业只要活下来就好；而新世代管理者则主张应打破惯例，继续加大投入，以寻求发展的新路径。面对新老世代管理者的碰撞，董事长巫艾玲该如何抉择？该案例所表现的新老世代管理者的决策冲突问题常见于现代企业，面对这种情况，企业最高决策者该如何抉择，这一问题典型且值得深入讨论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The issue of decision-making conflicts between the new and old generations is one of the common problems in modern management. The colored forest project under Chongqing Bangtian Agricultural Development Co., Ltd. is currently managed by two generations. When the external environment is facing significant changes, the new and old generations of managers will have different thinking and practical skills. From the perspective of Chairman Wu Ailing, this case describes the decision-making conflict between the new and old generations of managers of the company on whether to continue increasing investment in the face of the sudden decrease in revenue of Bangtian Agriculture under the impact of the epidemic. The old expert insists that we cannot continue to increase investment, believing that as long as the enterprise survives, it is good; The new generation of managers advocates breaking conventions and continuing to increase investment to seek new paths for development. How should Chairman Wu Ailing make a decision in the face of the collision between new and old generations of managers? The decision-making conflict problem of the new and old generations of managers represented in this case is common in modern enterprises. In the face of this situation, how the highest decision-maker of the enterprise should make a decision is a typical and worthy of in-depth discussion.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略选择；战略决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
